{"tid":2319904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九巴擋風玻璃遭塗污 藏噴漆女童認罪 判保護令可不留案底","createTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T11:59:40.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50df8bced58ee70752b625d3160f9c2902ee03c9","tid":2319904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"去年12月9日有網民再度呼籲三罷，早上各區多處出現混亂。其中在大埔有九巴擋風玻璃被示威者噴漆，警方其後拘捕一名手持噴漆的15歲女生。女生早前承認管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪，今日在粉嶺裁判法院少年法庭判刑。主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">蘇文隆</span>稱念在被告年輕，接納報告建議，判她接受18個月保護令，不留案底，但須賠償880元予九巴。<br />\n<br />\n蘇官並提醒被告「要聽話，唔係鎖你入屯門兒童院」，同時宣佈被告不留案底，但應控方要求，下令被告向九巴賠償880元。"},{"pid":"6f78b58a657f0f31875ab9e24b440035550be895","tid":2319904,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/DL5GHOTCUZF3BB36SBNPXLGPXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FDL5GHOTCUZF3BB36SBNPXLGPXY%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYplKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=125d9cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FDL5GHOTCUZF3BB36SBNPXLGPXY%2F&h=ed779433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/DL5GHOTCUZF3BB36SBNPXLGPXY/</a>"},{"pid":"7c3f7637dd36c0b487d2eaa2220abf67ba52bc65","tid":2319904,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:43:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50ed0ea5505d1b13e6e7a04798046aa3aefd9ea7","tid":2319904,"uid":300782,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"要聽話，唔係鎖你入屯門兒童院<br />\n<br />\n恐嚇呀？<br />\n咩叫聽話？邊條法例define?"},{"pid":"e17c33ff75433780fe457c21518396e7bf24235e","tid":2319904,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk